      <title>黄金股票闪闪发光，因为担心通货膨胀，关税爆发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/gold-stocks-glitter-as-worries-around-inflation-tariffs-flare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金矿工的股价在2025年初的早期飙升，因为围绕通货膨胀和地缘政治的风险推动分析师提高其对贵金属的外观，这是经典的避风港资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/gold-stocks-glitter-as-worries-around-inflation-tariffs-flare</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
